name: lazercan and microtaner
description: People died and only us remained. We are evolved looters, our purpose; we enjoy surviving by accessing what we can't get in the real world. It is not possible to estimate the population of the world at the moment, one thing I know is that there are no signs of life other than us within a radius of 30km. The number of animals has increased by an estimated 30% compared to 2021, cities have become their playground, and we have settled in the countryside. The world is better like this, the only thing missing is a beer that we can drink cold...
